# Scheduling Using Cron
Open Cron
```bash
crontab -e
```
Schedule the script every day at **1 PM**
```cron
0 13 * * * /home/ubuntu/shellscripts/health_report.sh
```
Verify Cron
```bash
crontab -l
```
---
# Log Files
The script generates one log file per day.
